text: Michel Liebgott (born February 15, 1958 in Algrange) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Moselle department, and is a member of the Socialiste, radical, citoyen et divers gauche. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:People from Algrange Category:Socialist Party (France) politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
title: Michel Liebgott
